### =====================================================================
### DataSeeder API  (base route: api/DataSeeder/)
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Seed Users (no body required)
POST {{host}}/api/DataSeeder/Users

### Seed Categories (no body required)
POST {{host}}/api/DataSeeder/Categories
